  "title": "Propositions & Strategy Lead, Emerging Markets",
  "description": "<p>What you’ll do: </p><ul><li><p>Support, shape and lead product & offer propositions that unlock growth across emerging markets, with a strong focus on premium user acquisition.</p></li><li><p>Work on complex, cross-functional initiatives end to end to support bringing to life partnerships, working closely with Product, Legal, Technical Accounting, FP&A and  supporting key stakeholders in regional sales teams.</p></li><li><p>Identify and ideate on audience expansion initiatives that balance user value, partner needs, commercial impact, and technical feasibility.</p></li><li><p>Drive alignment across global and regional stakeholders, ensuring partnership goals connect clearly to broader Spotify priorities & are supportive of reaching the broader teams sales targets.</p></li></ul><p>Who you are: </p><ul><li><p>You have a minimum of at least 12+ years experience in a strategic role working at the intersection of partnerships, product, and growth, and regional exposure.</p></li><li><p>You collaborate naturally across disciplines and regions, building alignment and momentum even when priorities compete.</p></li><li><p>You use data, insights, and experimentation to guide decisions, while also applying strong judgment when the path isn’t obvious.</p></li><li><p>You’re comfortable owning initiatives with real business impact and staying accountable from early concept through delivery.</p></li></ul>",
